TITLE: Pentagon Fires Back at Joe Biden: 'DOD Has Been Completely Transparent'
SUMMARY: The Pentagon responded to Biden's accusations that its leadership has been obstructing the transition process.

TITLE: Schumer to Kavanaugh and Gorsuch: ‘You Will Pay the Price’ – ‘Won’t Know What Hit You’ if You Make ‘Awful Decisions’
SUMMARY: During a speech about the abortion case before the Supreme Court on Wednesday, Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer (D-NY) stated to Supreme Court Justices Neil Gorsuch and Brett Kavanaugh, “you have released the whirlwind and you will pay the price.
